data.name: permitExperimentalFileAddingCB.Text
data.value:
Experimental - File Adding By default, RAF Manager will only allow you to pack files that already exist in the Originally, this was because a certain function was not documented by Riot. Now, that safety is still enabled, simply because most of the time (if not always), if you're trying to add a file that doesn't exist in the RAF archives, you're doing something wrong... ex: File got changed from Ezreal.dds to Ezreal_tx_cm.dds
This feature is highly unrecommended for the novice user. Expect to have to restore your RAF Archives (in other words, make sure that you have backed up your files!)
